            The only requirements is that you understand the basics of HTML,
            CSS, Eleventy, Nunjucks templating, and basic English.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/surfscape"
            class="sk-button sk-button-ocean"
            >Access our Github</a
          >
        </section>
