            Use our 88x31 button!
          </p>
          <pre><code>&lt;a href="https://surfscape.neocities.org"&gt;
  &lt;img src="https://yourwebsite.com/images/btn_surfscape.png" alt="SurfScape button"&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;
</code></pre>
